  Ah! Oan5-lah. Chiu7-si7 tang5 hit-si5 li2 ia7 kho2-i2 khoaN3-kiN3 hu7-kin7 soaN-pho e5 lek8-chhau2-pou teng2, siong5-siong5 u7 chit8-ui7 ho5-sian7 e5 lau7-lang5 un2-ku, giah8 tioh8 chit8-ki koaiN2-a2 un-un-a2 tong7, ban7-ban7-a2 kiaN5. I chiong sin bo5 chhoa7 choe3 koan-hu. Choan-bun5 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7 thoe3 lang5 choe3 iu2-ek e5 su7, tham3 peN7 lang5, thoe3 lang5 kai2-koat lan5-te5, an-ui3 iu-siong e5 lang5, tek8-piat8 si7 tui3 ti7 loan5-ai3 tiong, kap pi7 lang5 loan5-ai3 ui5-khi3 e5 lang5, ka7 in pang-bang5. Hoan7-na7 tu2-tioh8 lang5 teh khoaN3-khin lam5-lu2 loan5-ai3 choe3 thang kian3-siau3 kho2-phi2 e5 su7 hit-si5, liah8 choe3 m7-thang tui3 lang5 kong2 chhut, liah8 choe3 liau2 hit-ho7 si5-kan si7 bo5 ke3-tat8 e5 si5, i it-teng7 tui3 seng-khu theh8 chhut seng3-keng, hian Su3-tou5 heng7-toan7 sou2 ki3 Pi2-tek sou2 khoaN3 e5 iN7-siong7 kong2:
  ¡§¡K¡KU7 siaN-im ng3 i kong2, Pi2-tek khi2--lai5, thai5 lai5 chiah8, Pi2-tek the-si5 kong2, Chu2 ah! Che si7 m7-thang, kiN3-na7 chhou-siok8 e5 mih8 kap bo5 chheng-khi3 e5 mih8, goa2 chiong5-lai5 m7-bat chiah8. Te7 2 pai2 u7 siaN ng3 i kong2, Siong7-te3 sou2 hou7 i chheng-khi3 e5, li2 m7-thang liah8 choe3 chhou-siok8 e5 mih8¡K¡K¡¨ 
  Thak8 chit cham7 liau2, hit ui7 lau7-lang5 chiu7 e7 tui3 chit8 pan chheng-lian5 kong2, eng2-oan2 m7-thang liah8 ¡§Loan5-ai3¡¨ choe3 kian3-siau3. M7-thang liah8 chheng-lian5 lam5-lu2 chhin-chhiat iu2-gi5-tek e5 cheng5-ai3, kap hu-hu7 loan5-ai3 e5 thiaN3-cheng5 choe3 kian3-siau3. Siong7-te3 ki3-jian5 hou7 ai3-cheng5 chiaN5-choe3 chheng-khi3, lan2 kiam2 thang khoaN3 i choe3 kiaN lang5, kho2-thi2? M7-thang, in-ui7 Siong7-te3 chiu7-si7 thiaN3, ji5-chhiaN2 Siong7-te3 sou2 cho7 tak8-hang7 su7-but8 e5 tiong-kan, thiaN3 si7 choe3 kho2-ai3 e5, hian7-kim sou2 chun5 u7 sin3, u7 ng3-bang7, u7 jin5-ai3, ki5-tiong choe3 te7-it toa7 e5 chiu7-si7 ¡§ThiaN3.¡¨ Sou2-i2 se3-kiaN2 ah! Tioh8 saN-thiaN3, peng3-chhiaN2 ai3 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 lin2 kho2-i2 pi2-chhu2 saN-thiaN3. Chheng-lian5 lang5 thiaN i kong2 chiah e5 oe7, tai7-ke long2 chin hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8. Na7-si7 bo5 chit8 e5 chai chit ui7 lau7-lang5 si7 hui3-liau2 goa7 toa7 e5 tai7-ke3 chiah lai5 oh8 chit kho3 e5 kau3-hun3. (Oan5) 
